<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="wallcache Photography by Hal Wall - Quiet scenes, unhurried light, attention to ordinary beauty. Based in Barnes, London.">
    <title>wallcache Photography | Hal Wall</title>

    <!-- Favicons -->
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="assets/images/favicons/favicon-32x32.png">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="assets/images/favicons/favicon-16x16.png">
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="assets/images/favicons/apple-touch-icon.png">

    <!-- Adobe Fonts -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://use.typekit.net/ffk6gen.css">

    <!-- Stylesheet -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="assets/css/styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Header / Navigation -->
    <header>
        <nav>
            <a href="index.html" class="logo">
                <img src="assets/images/logos/wallcache-logo.png" alt="wallcache Logo">
            </a>

            <ul class="nav-links">
                <li><a href="cv.html">CV</a></li>
                <li><a href="projects.html">Projects</a></li>
                <li class="dropdown">
                    <a href="writing/index.html">Writing ▾</a>
                    <div class="dropdown-content">
                        <a href="writing/blog.html">Blog</a>
                        <a href="writing/book-reviews.html">Book Reviews</a>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li><a href="wallcache.html">wallcache</a></li>
            </ul>

            <button class="mobile-menu-toggle" aria-label="Toggle menu">☰</button>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <!-- Page Header -->
    <section class="hero" style="min-height: 70vh;">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <div style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                <img src="assets/images/logos/2wallcache-logo.png" alt="wallcache Logo" style="max-width: 300px; height: auto;">
            </div>
            <h1 class="tilt-heavy">wallcache</h1>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Brand Statement -->
    <section>
        <div class="container-narrow">
            <div class="paper-card text-center">
                <p style="font-size: 1.3rem; line-height: 1.9;">
                    Photography as an exercise in attention. Quiet scenes, unhurried light, the strange
                    beauty of ordinary things. No rushing, no performance—just paying close attention
                    to what's actually there.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- About Section -->
    <section class="blueprint-grid">
        <div class="container-narrow">
            <div class="navy-card">
                <h2 class="tilt-light handwriting">About the Work</h2>
                <p style="margin-top: 1.5rem; line-height: 1.8;">
                    I'm drawn to compositions that ask you to stay a moment longer. Empty spaces where
                    light does something interesting. The texture of a day you nearly walked past. This
                    is work about seeing clearly, not saying something clever.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Gallery -->
    <section>
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="tilt-light mb-xl text-center">Selected Work</h2>

            <div class="photo-gallery">
                <!-- Placeholder photo items with sketch borders -->
                <div class="photo-item sketch-border">
                    <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; height: 100%; color: var(--charcoal); font-size: 3rem; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e0e0e0, #f5f5f5);">
                        📷
                    </div>
                    <div class="photo-caption">
                        <span class="handwriting">Richmond Park, morning light</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="photo-item sketch-border">
                    <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; height: 100%; color: var(--charcoal); font-size: 3rem; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #d0d0d0, #e5e5e5);">
                        🌆
                    </div>
                    <div class="photo-caption">
                        <span class="handwriting">Thames at dusk</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="photo-item sketch-border">
                    <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; height: 100%; color: var(--charcoal); font-size: 3rem; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e5e5e5, #f0f0f0);">
                        🏛️
                    </div>
                    <div class="photo-caption">
                        <span class="handwriting">Architectural detail</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="photo-item sketch-border">
                    <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; height: 100%; color: var(--charcoal); font-size: 3rem; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dadada, #ebebeb);">
                        🌿
                    </div>
                    <div class="photo-caption">
                        <span class="handwriting">Garden study</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="photo-item sketch-border">
                    <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; height: 100%; color: var(--charcoal); font-size: 3rem; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #c5c5c5, #e0e0e0);">
                        👤
                    </div>
                    <div class="photo-caption">
                        <span class="handwriting">Portrait session</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="photo-item sketch-border">
                    <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; height: 100%; color: var(--charcoal); font-size: 3rem; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e8e8e8, #f3f3f3);">
                        📚
                    </div>
                    <div class="photo-caption">
                        <span class="handwriting">Still life composition</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Approach -->
    <section class="blueprint-grid">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="tilt-light mb-xl text-center">How I Work</h2>

            <div class="grid grid-2">
                <div class="paper-card">
                    <h3 class="handwriting tilt-light">Technical</h3>
                    <p>
                        I shoot with professional full-frame cameras and a range of prime and zoom lenses
                        to suit different situations. My technical background helps me adapt quickly to
                        changing lighting conditions and challenging environments.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Every session includes professional editing and color grading. I deliver images
                        that are polished yet natural, enhancing rather than transforming the scene.
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="paper-card">
                    <h3 class="handwriting tilt-light">Creative</h3>
                    <p>
                        Great photography happens at the intersection of preparation and spontaneity.
                        While I always have a shot list and plan, the best moments often emerge
                        unexpectedly.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        My goal is to create images that feel authentic and timeless. Trends come and go,
                        but honest photography that captures genuine emotion and beautiful light will
                        always resonate.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Services -->
    <section>
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="tilt-light mb-xl text-center">Services</h2>

            <div class="grid grid-3">
                <div class="navy-card">
                    <h3 class="handwriting tilt-light">Portraits</h3>
                    <p>
                        Professional headshots, personal branding photography, and creative portrait
                        sessions. Helping individuals present their best selves.
                    </p>
                    <div class="annotation" style="margin-top: 1rem;">From £200</div>
                </div>

                <div class="navy-card">
                    <h3 class="handwriting tilt-light">Events</h3>
                    <p>
                        Coverage for corporate events, conferences, private celebrations, and special
                        occasions. Documenting moments that matter.
                    </p>
                    <div class="annotation" style="margin-top: 1rem;">From £400</div>
                </div>

                <div class="navy-card">
                    <h3 class="handwriting tilt-light">Commercial</h3>
                    <p>
                        Product photography, brand content, and commercial assignments for businesses
                        and creative professionals.
                    </p>
                    <div class="annotation" style="margin-top: 1rem;">Custom pricing</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Contact / Booking -->
    <section class="blueprint-grid">
        <div class="container-narrow">
            <div class="paper-card text-center">
                <h2 class="tilt-light">Book a Session</h2>
                <p style="margin-top: 1rem; line-height: 1.8;">
                    Interested in working together? I'd love to hear about your project. Send me a
                    message with details about what you're looking for, and I'll get back to you
                    with availability and pricing.
                </p>
                <div style="margin-top: 2rem;">
                    <a href="mailto:photography@wallcache.com" class="btn btn-primary">
                        Email Me
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="footer-content">
                <div class="footer-section">
                    <h3>Hal Wall</h3>
                    <p>
                        Data Engineer, photographer, and writer based in Barnes, London.
                    </p>
                    <div class="social-links">
                        <a href="#" aria-label="Instagram">IG</a>
                        <a href="#" aria-label="LinkedIn">in</a>
                        <a href="#" aria-label="GitHub">gh</a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="footer-section">
                    <h3>Navigation</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li><a href="cv.html">CV</a></li>
                        <li><a href="projects.html">Projects</a></li>
                        <li><a href="writing/index.html">Writing</a></li>
                        <li><a href="wallcache.html">wallcache</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="footer-section">
                    <h3>Projects</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li><a href="projects.html#long-form-press">Long Form Press</a></li>
                        <li><a href="wallcache.html">wallcache Photography</a></li>
                        <li><a href="projects.html">Data Engineering Work</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="footer-section">
                    <h3>Writing</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li><a href="writing/blog.html">Blog</a></li>
                        <li><a href="writing/book-reviews.html">Book Reviews</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="footer-bottom">
                <p>&copy; 2024 Hal Wall. All rights reserved.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <!-- JavaScript -->
    <script src="assets/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
